== 開發環境 ==
Adobe公司提供三種方式開發AIR應用軟件：
*[[HTML|HTML]]/[[Ajax|Ajax]]，或者利用Adobe Dreamweaver CC，其他HTML編輯器或文本編輯器結合AIR的SDK。<ref name="Adobe AIR SDK">{{cite web | url = http://www.adobe.com/devnet/air/ajax/getting_started.html | title = Adobe AIR Developer Center for HTML and Ajax - Getting Started | accessdate = 2008-02-26 | archive-date = 2008-02-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080220123035/http://www.adobe.com/devnet/air/ajax/getting_started.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>
*[[Adobe_Flex|Flex Builder 3]]
[[Adobe_Animate|Animate]]
*[[Adobe_Flash_Builder_4|Flash Builder 4]]

[[Adobe_Dreamweaver|Dreamweaver CS5]]需要安装额外的扩展程序才能创建AIR应用，<ref name="Dreamweaver">{{cite web | url = http://www.adobe.com/products/air/tools/ajax/#section-2 | title = Adobe - AIR: Tools for Ajax | accessdate = 2008-02-25 | archive-date = 2008-02-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080228042608/http://www.adobe.com/products/air/tools/ajax/#section-2 | dead-url = no }}</ref> [[Adobe_Flash|Flash CS3]]则需要升级才可使用。<ref name="Flash">{{cite web| url = http://www.adobe.com/support/flash/downloads.html#flashCS4| title = Adobe Flash - Downloads| accessdate = 2008-02-25| archive-date = 2008-02-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080222233900/http://www.adobe.com/support/flash/downloads.html#flashCS4| dead-url = no}}</ref>该运行环境跨平台的特性意味着，只要搭配上AIR SDK，任何网页编辑器都可以创建AIR应用。AIR自身使用[[WebKit|WebKit]]网页渲染引擎，同时还使用了Flash和PDF技术。

